MrRobotOS is built on top of the Linux kernel and contains
components that carry their own license obligations. This
file exists to be transparent about what belongs to whom.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
LINUX KERNEL & KERNEL MODULES                    [ GPL-2.0 ]
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The Linux kernel is licensed under GPL-2.0. MrRobotOS ships
a hardened and patched kernel build but does not claim
authorship over the kernel itself. The kernel source, its
authors, and its license are its own.

See: LICENSES/GPL-2.0

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
MRROBOTOS ORIGINAL WORK                          [ GPL-3.0 ]
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Every other component in this repository — the window
manager, the terminal, the status bar, the login manager,
the settings application, the process manager, the quick
settings panel, the calendar, the calculator, the power
menu, the application launcher, the panel scripts, the
system services, the init scripts, the autostart
configuration, and the ISO build system — was written from
scratch as part of MrRobotOS.

This work is licensed under GPL-3.0. You are free to use,
study, modify, and distribute it — but any distribution
must carry the same freedom forward.

See: LICENSES/GPL-3.0

